data.description: Welcome Home! Step inside this stunning 4 bed 2 bath relaxing oasis. Recently renovated throughout with brand new Furnace, Air Conditioning, Hot Water Heater, Electrical Panel and a Brand New Roof is going to be installed prior to Closing. Imagine a seamless Inspection and a smooth transaction all the way to Closing. With a Brand New Construction community being built right behind the neighborhood, home values are sure to rise! Conveniently located near Fort Carson Army Base, Peterson Space Force Base and the Academy Shopping Centers!  Don't miss your opportunity to get into this home before home prices rise too. Schedule your Private Tour on this home Today. This home will not last!
